<br>
2.  Damage Add Song - for the love of Odin, at least extend the range to 1500 units, though 2000 would be more appropriate.  700 units is absolute bs.<br>
<br>
3.  Reduce the power consumption of our DD's by 25%.<br>
<br>
4.  Pair up the Resist songs.  Make it so one Skald can sing one song that enhances 2 or even 3 resistances at a time.<br>
<br>
5.  Buff up the Health regen song.<br>
<br>
6.  Group speed song should break only when the Skald is hit.  There should be no lapsed pulses and it shouldn't break when a group member is hit.<br>
<br>
7.  Increase our spec pts to 1.75 per level so we can invest a few more points into Parry.<br>
<br>
These are the things Skalds want and need.  None of these will make us uber soloers, they will, however, make us more a more effective support class and secondary meleer.<br>
<br>
Its time that Mythic stopped ignoring Skalds because they happened to get it right initially with them.<br>
<br>
