<br>
Non 1.54 my top issues (drumroll)<br>
<br>
1.  Extend range of DD, or add ANYTHING that would make skalds effective in keep taking/defense.<br>
<br>
2.  Fix damage add stacking issues (less damage with shammy dmg add specifically)<br>
<br>
3.  FoG and the whole RAs in general need a complete overhaul.  I agree that FoG should be an effective counter against Bunker of Faith.  The lack of usefull unique RAs doesn't balance RvR it creates inherent imbalances.  Copy Paste Speed of Sound for skalds.  Anything useful and actually works.  I also agree with mastery of arcane comment.<br>
<br>
4.  My idead to fix the Dark Age of Assassins problem.  Add a PBAOE unstealth song for skalds, bards, and minstrels.  With the time to restealth varies as a function of distance.  Assassins need something to fear.<br>
<br>
5.  Fix Rest Songs.  LvL 4 rest song should significantly reduce downtimes while at rest at least.  Would like to see it along the lines of the Pali heal song.<br>
<br>
6.  Adjust HP/ add Evade 2 (ask for 3 heh) Increase spec to 1.7.  Toe to toe a Pure Melee &gt; Hybrid &gt; Rogue &gt; Support &gt; casters as far as dealing and taking melee damage.  Bards and minstrels are hurting as well. I'd suggest increasing skald's melee capabilities, and increasing Min/Bard support capabilities.<br>
<br>
7.  Speed song should not be affected by damage taken to other members of grp.  It should only drop when the skald his/herself takes damage/ neg effect. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/bteamskald.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hooliganfriar>hooliganfriar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#ff0000>(11/6/02 10:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=384.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Skald Report - Coming soon!</span><hr size=1> non 1.54 specific<br>
<br>
The only things I want other than the bug fixes that have been mentioned many times is:<br>
<br>
1. Reduce the recast timer on the dd spells. I think its 20 seconds. I wish it was 15 seconds. I don't think the endurance or power usage needs to be changed. This would help on a lot of close fights especially with the way resists seem to effect our dd now.<br>
<br>
2. Medium shields. We are a viking class and should be able to block a little better. I don't think we should get to spec shields but being able to block multiple enemys would be nice. It would also maybe give us a reason to go sword and board instead of 2-handed. Also I don't think higher evade is the answer either. We are not a rogue class.<br>
<br>
3. Increase our dmg add song in both effectiveness and range. Midgard doesn't have as good of a dmg add as the other realms, in any of our classes. It doesnt have to be as good as the wizards dmg add but maybe a little bump up would be nice just to make it worth it for a shammy or runie to stack with ours even if they are not full specced in the dmg add. The range is pathetic. The only person being helped by this song in a fight is  me. It would be nice if if the zerkers, warriors and thanes got a piece of this song once in a while. <br>
<br>
<br>
Thats about it. I know a lot of people want way more than I do but I doubt they will give us anything at all until the expansion. Mythic may try to fix a lot of balance issues with the new classes. <br>
<br>
p.s. oh ya almost forgot. One of my biggest wishes is for everyone to stop comparing us to bards and minstrels. We have more in common with pallies and wardens than bards or minstrels. WE ARE A CHANTING CLASS! NOT A MUSICIAN CLASS! WE DONT USE ANY SISSY INSTRUMENTS! heh. <p>Hooligan lvl 43 friar bedevere&lt;BR&gt;<br>
