<br>
However, if you look at the numbers, skalds (and minstrels) are using an unfair &quot;damage to power table&quot;. Their shouts cost twice as much power as they should, compared to any other classes in the game.<br>
<br>
Though I have not tested it (and it is hard to test because there are no numerical values at all for endurance), I strongly suspect the endurance usage is tied to the power cost, and thus, minstrels and skalds pay twice as much endurance as they should. I think this suggestion should be considered. Without asking more or less reasonable upgrades, putting skald shouts on a reasonable power and endurance cost would do wonders for the class. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#efe0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/bteamskald.showUserPublicProfile?gid=drgenocide>DrGenocide</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Participant</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#ff0000>(11/13/02 9:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=384.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The End</span><hr size=1> Roseanna, <br>
